channel.title: Need an experienced programmer for new server!
channel.description: Hello, if you're interested I was wondering whether someone could be a programmer for a new RSPS me and my friend are planning to release in the next 4 weeks or so. We have big hopes for a new server to kick off and have very good ideas which you could implement into the server. I dont believe anything major will need to be done, its just generally a lot of tweaks to other standard servers. Get back to me asap with a reply or even inbox The name is heiko123 Also if i get no replies in the next 48 hours i will be asking another friend of mine. Thanks and Good - Luck who gets picked :)
